# =============================================================================
# outreach-credify — environment reference. NAMES ONLY, never real values.
# =============================================================================
# The real file lives on the server at /etc/credify/outreach.env — OUTSIDE
# the web root — and is loaded by src/server.js via the ENV_FILE path.
# .env is gitignored. If it ever appears in `git status`, stop and fix it.
# Nothing runs on a local machine (see CLAUDE.md), so no local .env exists.

# --- Database ----------------------------------------------------------------
# NOTE: Postgres listens on the NON-DEFAULT port 5433 on this server.
DATABASE_URL=postgresql://USER:PASSWORD@127.0.0.1:5433/credify_cluster_email

# --- Listener: set exactly ONE of the two -----------------------------------
# Default — unix domain socket behind nginx:
SOCKET_PATH=/run/credify/outreach.sock
# Rollback escape hatch — loopback TCP (pair with the nginx upstream change;
# see CLAUDE.md "Rollback escape hatch"):
# PORT=3001

# --- Optional ----------------------------------------------------------------
# Override where the server looks for this file (defaults to the path above):
# ENV_FILE=/etc/credify/outreach.env
